{"tid":382367,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"「去性化」中性內衣是什麼概念","createTime":"2017-08-31T15:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T18:40:39.000Z","uid":14730,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"267b6ad0e4788f7b4c48e19cb7f159545b8b371f","tid":382367,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T15:47:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/234732_00b3ef38025afa99848652aff4a9133a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F234732_00b3ef38025afa99848652aff4a9133a.jpg&h=2e9b07fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n還記得兩年前落戶倫敦的香港設計師Marie Yat，以反性化內衣的設計概念，推出「去性化」中性內衣系列，以舒適與不對社會標籤妥協的原則作為設計目標，內衣大多是無縫無鋼線的純棉設計，不刻意調整身材，引來一陣熱烈討論。論調大多指概念有趣，設計上帶有九十年代Calvin Klein的美學，但影像上還是有衝擊的性感視覺，使品牌惹多正反兩極討論。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n最近內衣品牌Agent Provocateur創辦人之一的Serena Rees，發佈另一新內衣品牌Les Girls Les Boys，以「去性化」中性內衣作為招徠，與一直以極度女性化，大量運用性挑逗作為美學基準的Agent Provocateur幾近完全相反。比起Marie Yat的設計，Les Girls Les Boys更為簡潔而不加修飾，希望內衣設計完全與「性」脫離關係，成為純功能性的衣飾單品。<br />\n <br />\n來源：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2wLSbWY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2wLSbWY&d=aTI0xW5AaQCkVNzvabHkVMmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=e8bd5188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2wLSbWY</a>"},{"pid":"beeec5e2b048c090271b894421ce461f7748337e","tid":382367,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T18:33:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c8906e1622502bf7df15360abcfd411f5459a23","tid":382367,"uid":988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T18:39:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f37626755d9d9373277ff974ae43a76c0c558b6","tid":382367,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T18:40:39.000Z","msg":"日本高中泳衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}